name: Medusa Stone Roots
description:
I did not turn to stone but I did turn into an admirer and Medusa has become a muse of many of my creation's.
-Menace2Metaverse
The image of Medusa was thought to be protective. Ancient statuary, bronze shields, and vessels have depictions of Medusa. Famous artists that have been inspired by Medusa and the heroic Perseus story include Leonardo da Vinci, Benvenuto Cellini, Peter Paul Rubens, Gialorenzo Bernini, Pablo Picasso, Auguste Rodin, and Salvador Dali.
